{
  "texts": [
    "This context is then added to the main task, or set of tasks, that the dialogue manager defines based on the user's request.",
    "It is noticeable that this arrangement of the final prompt demands a larger volume of text to be transferred to the LLM.",
    "This is a compromise that we find necessary to reduce the risk of generating irrelevant outputs, even if the output is not wrong.",
    "Depending on the LLM used, the allowed size of context may differ, limiting the amount of contextual text that can be added to the prompt.",
    "Proof-of-Concept Evaluation and ResultsTo evaluate the system, we test first the performance of the proposed intent classifier."
  ]
